text: Demetra Dias #1,524 Most Popular About TikTok star, online content creator, and social media personality who is known for her demetradias TikTok account, which has gained 4.5 million followers. She has frequently posted videos showcasing different casual outfits. She has often worn light blue jeans in her videos. Before fame She began posting to her demetra.dias Instagram account in late 2022. Her first post was a picture of her wearing a dark purple dress. Trivia One of her hobbies is skiing. She is a fan of the 2007 film Ratatouille. She primarily posts lifestyle and fashion-themed content on her popular demetra.dias Instagram account. She has also done unboxing videos, which have featured fashion brands like Hollister and American Eagle. Family life She was romantically linked to Pierce Finkle. She is currently dating Hudson Cryder. Associated with In December of 2023, she posted a TikTok lip-sync video set to the song "Pink Friday Girls" by Nicki Minaj.
